<ul>
<li>Simplified method of quilting cutoff cups;</li>
<li>Back divided to 4 parts, for a better fitting for a complex body type;</li>
<li>Using hard synthetic corset net.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Skills you gain:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Constructing light and strong bases for embossed drapery;</li>
<li>Easy method to put on the drapery and secure it on the corset;</li>
<li>Clean way to close folds with lacing bar.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Where to use:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Widely used technology for creating wedding (and evening) dresses Haute Couture.</li>
